<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,624,728]" pageId="4" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,465,624,650]" pageId="4" pageNumber="31">Distribution and habitat:</emphasis>
—This species shares a similar distribution with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="F. M. Ferreira &amp; R. P. Oliveira" baseAuthorityName="Trinius" baseAuthorityYear="1834" box="[1040,1297,625,650]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Parianella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="4" pageNumber="31" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lanceolata">
<emphasis box="[1040,1297,625,650]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="31">Parianella lanceolata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in southern 
<collectingRegion box="[151,222,664,690]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="4" pageNumber="31">Bahia</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[233,307,664,690]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="31">Brazil</collectingCountry>
, but only a single population is known (
<bibRefCitation author="Oliveira, R. P. &amp; Longhi-Wagner, H. M. &amp; Leite, K. R. B. &amp; Hollowell, V. C." box="[771,996,664,690]" pageId="4" pageNumber="31" pagination="262 - 266" refId="ref2931" refString="Oliveira, R. P., Longhi-Wagner, H. M., Leite, K. R. B. &amp; Hollowell, V. C. (2008) Pariana multiflora (Poaceae, Bambusoideae, Olyreae), a new species from eastern Brazil, with notes on the leaf anatomy of the genus. Systematic Botany 33: 262 - 266. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1600 / 036364408784571617" type="journal article" year="2008">
Oliveira 
<emphasis box="[876,927,664,689]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="31">et al</emphasis>
2008
</bibRefCitation>
). For this reason, it was recently cited among the rare plant species of 
<collectingCountry box="[523,594,702,728]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="31">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Oliveira &amp; Longhi-Wagner" authorityYear="2004" box="[644,859,703,728]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Pariana" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="4" pageNumber="31" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="carvalhoi">
<emphasis box="[644,859,703,728]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="31">Pariana carvalhoi</emphasis>
